#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="an7.19"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an7.19:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 7 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 7 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an7.19:0.2"
msgid "2. Anusayavagga "
msgstr "2. Tendencies "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an7.19:0.3"
msgid "19. Nibbānasutta "
msgstr "19. Extinguishment "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "an7.19:1.1"
msgid "“Nibbāne sukhānupassī viharati sukhasaññī sukhapaṭisaṃvedī satataṃ samitaṃ abbokiṇṇaṃ cetasā adhimuccamāno paññāya pariyogāhamāno. "
msgstr "“First, take a person who meditates observing the happiness in extinguishment. They perceive happiness and experience happiness. Constantly, continually, and without stopping, they apply the mind and fathom with wisdom. "

msgctxt "an7.19:1.2"
msgid "So āsavānaṃ khayā … pe … sacchikatvā upasampajja viharati. "
msgstr "They’ve realized the undefiled freedom of heart and freedom by wisdom in this very life, and live having realized it with their own insight due to the ending of defilements. "

msgctxt "an7.19:1.3"
msgid "Ayaṃ bhikkhave, paṭhamo puggalo āhuneyyo … pe … puññakkhettaṃ lokassa. "
msgstr "This is the first person worthy of offerings. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "an7.19:2.1"
msgid "Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, idhekacco puggalo nibbāne sukhānupassī viharati sukhasaññī sukhapaṭisaṃvedī satataṃ samitaṃ abbokiṇṇaṃ cetasā adhimuccamāno paññāya pariyogāhamāno. "
msgstr "Next, take a person who meditates observing the happiness in extinguishment. They perceive happiness and experience happiness. Constantly, continually, and without stopping, they apply the mind and fathom with wisdom. "

msgctxt "an7.19:2.2"
msgid "Tassa apubbaṃ acarimaṃ āsavapariyādānañca hoti jīvitapariyādānañca. "
msgstr "Their defilements and their life come to an end at exactly the same time. "

msgctxt "an7.19:2.3"
msgid "Ayaṃ, bhikkhave, dutiyo puggalo āhuneyyo … pe … anuttaraṃ puññakkhettaṃ lokassa. "
msgstr "This is the second person. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli4.15, sc3
msgctxt "an7.19:3.1"
msgid "Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, idhekacco puggalo nibbāne sukhānupassī viharati sukhasaññī sukhapaṭisaṃvedī satataṃ samitaṃ abbokiṇṇaṃ cetasā adhimuccamāno paññāya pariyogāhamāno. "
msgstr "Next, take a person who meditates observing the happiness in extinguishment. They perceive happiness and experience happiness. Constantly, continually, and without stopping, they apply the mind and fathom with wisdom. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an7.19:3.2"
msgid "So pañcannaṃ orambhāgiyānaṃ saṃyojanānaṃ parikkhayā antarāparinibbāyī hoti … pe … "
msgstr "With the ending of the five lower fetters they’re extinguished between one life and the next. … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an7.19:3.3"
msgid "upahaccaparinibbāyī hoti … pe … "
msgstr "With the ending of the five lower fetters they’re extinguished upon landing. … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an7.19:3.4"
msgid "asaṅkhāraparinibbāyī hoti … pe … "
msgstr "With the ending of the five lower fetters they’re extinguished without extra effort. … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an7.19:3.5"
msgid "sasaṅkhāraparinibbāyī hoti … pe … "
msgstr "With the ending of the five lower fetters they’re extinguished with extra effort. … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an7.19:3.6"
msgid "uddhaṃsoto hoti akaniṭṭhagāmī. "
msgstr "With the ending of the five lower fetters they head upstream, going to the Akaniṭṭha realm. "

msgctxt "an7.19:3.7"
msgid "Ayaṃ, bhikkhave, sattamo puggalo āhuneyyo … pe … anuttaraṃ puññakkhettaṃ lokassa. "
msgstr "This is the seventh person. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an7.19:3.8"
msgid "Ime kho, bhikkhave, satta puggalā āhuneyyā … pe … anuttaraṃ puññakkhettaṃ lokassā”ti. "
msgstr "These are the seven people who are worthy of offerings dedicated to the gods, worthy of hospitality, worthy of a religious donation, worthy of greeting with joined palms, and are the supreme field of merit for the world.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an7.19:3.9"
msgid "Navamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

